                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The ravener breathes a blast of necrotic flame that deals @Damage[20d6[fire]] damage plus @Damage[4d6[persistent,void]] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:44|basic|options:area-effect,inflicts:drained] save). A creature that fails its save is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1} (or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2} on a critical failure). If a creature is drained by the ravener's Void Breath, the ravener's soul ward gains 5 HP. The ravener can't use Void Breath again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Void Breath]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
